quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  40,8,"Mala'ika'en wi'a kadi: Joomi amen, naadu gom…óim…ìe …ìen ka Aljannaaji √±ii…ìal, …óin …ói fodu…óaa …ìe, wa…ótidaa…ìe e kala mo∆¥∆¥inno…óo golle, immorde e baabiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe, e genndiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe, e …ìi…ó…ìe ma…ì…ìe. Pellet, ko An woni Foolu…óo Mo gooto foolataa, √ëee√±u…óo e e…ì…ìoore e toppitannde Mun."
  40,9,"Da…óndaa …ìe golle ma…ì…ìe bon…óe …óen, hara A nanngitiraali …ìe …óen. Kala non da…óndu…óaa …óum √ëalnde Darngal, haray A yuminii mo. Ko …óum woni malal mawnungal ngal sugu mun alaa."
  40,10,"Yeddu…ìe e Nulaa…óo Makko on, noddoyte √ëalnde Darngal, tuma …ìe naadaa ka Yiite, …ìe tikkana ko'e ma…ì…ìe, haa …ìe fe√±√±ina …óum, wonnde: ko tikkere Allah nden, …ìuri mawnude e dii ko tikkan…óon ko'e mon kon, tuma noddeteno…óon aduna, e fii gom…óingol Allah, yeddon Mo, kafidon Mo e rewetee…ói goo."
  40,11,"Yeddu…ì …ìen qirritoo junuubi ma…ì…ìe …óin, ka qirritagol tuuba nafataa, …ìe wi'a: joomi amen, A warii men laawi …ói…ói, tawde men woodanooko, tagu…óaa Men, refti waru…óaa men …ìaawo …óum. Wuurnitu…óaa men kadi laawi …ói…ói, ka tawnoo men woodanooka, e ka wuurnitu…óaa men …óon ummital. Haray men qirrike junuubi …ói men faggitii …óin. Taw si laawol no woodi, ka men yaltira e ngee Yiite, men yiltitoo aduna, fii mo∆¥∆¥ingol golle amen, ja…ìanaa men …óe?"
  40,12,"∆äen lepte …óe leptira…óon, ko sabu tawde si Allah tun noddanooma, hara O sirkanaaka, on yeddayno …óum, wa…óanon Mo kafidii…ói; si tawii non O kafidaama, gom…óinon. Awa √±aawoore nden, ko Kanko tun heeranii, On Toowu…óo e Jaati Mun e Kattal Mun, Mawnu…óo e hoore kala huunde."
  40,13,"Ko Allah tun woni holliroowo on maandeeji Makko …óin, ka tatteeri(jookli) e ka wonkiiji, ko …ìannginana on, Kattal e Gootaagu Makko. O jippinirana on to…ìo ka kammu, fii ko arsikire…óon, immorde e pu…ói e remuruuji ewk. Alaa non waajitoroowo maandeeji Allah …óin, si wanaa tuuboowo la…ì…ìina, ruttoo e Makko on."
  40,14,"Onon …ìee gom…óim…ìe, rewiree Allah, la…ì…ìinirangol Mo dewal e toraare, hara on kafidaali Mo e go…ó…óum, hay si tawii …óum welataa heefer…ìe …ìen."
  40,15,"Ko Kanko hanndi heertinaneede toraare e …óoftaare, tawde ko O Jom darjaaji toowu…ói …ìanngi e kala tagu Makko ngun, Jey…óo Arsi maw…óo on. Himo jippinira wahayu on, e mo o muuyani e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, no pittaali ma…ì…ìe wuurira, …ìe wuurniira …óum wo…ó…ìe goo, e fii yo jertinir yim…ìe …ìen, √ëalnde Darngal, nde aram…ìe e sakkitii…ìe hawroyta."
  40,16,"√ëalnde …ìe fee√±oyta nden, hara hi…ìe moo…ìondiri e nokku gooto. Huunde suu…óotaako Allah, e fii ma…ì…ìe, wanaa kam…ìe, wanaa golle ma…ì…ìe …óen, wanaa kadi njo…ìdi ma…ì…ìe ndin."